{
  "stem": "8252.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With Michael Librach in Scarsdale, New York.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Today is November 2nd, 1995, and I'm Terry Tull.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Michael, you just described a pretty harrowing journey out of Lodz to France.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's January, 1940, and you have just entered the Polish Army in exile--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in France, which is a part of the French Army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went to the front about April-- April, '40-- '40.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In April '40, we went covering their [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] space in between the Maginot Line, and we were first of our division to cover.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had been covering a Senegalese infantry in front of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, you know, this was, like, mid-April, and the Germans, when they started the push, which was beginning of-- end of May, I think, or something like that, they started the big push just to overrun France, and that's where they came through.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so we were there, the Senegalese run away, and we were shooting at the Germans-- German infantry with 75-millimeter guns, which are very unwieldy for this kind of fighting.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was mostly towards-- very close to Alsace-Lorraine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was not directly in Alsace-Lorraine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were a little west of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Finally, one day we found out that we are completely surrounded.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And our officers told us to just drop the arms and try to penetrate through the lines into southern France.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The French army would be-- start reconstructing itself there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so we were walking very stupidly on a ridge, on top of a ridge, and there was a French soldier in front of us screaming [FRENCH].",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Here, come here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we thought that he's just directing us how to get through.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
